## 4. 🏗️ Proposed Architecture (CDIA v2)

| Layer | Component | Mathematical Function |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **1. Perception** | **Equivariant Scene Graph** | Maps pixels to $SE(3)$ object poses. $f: \text{Image} \to \text{Graph}$. |
| **2. Cognition** | **Dynamic Graph ODE** | Evolves adjacency $A(t)$ to route information. Sparse MoE. |
| **3. Policy** | **Diffusion + CBF** | Generates trajectory candidates, projects to safe set via QP. |
| **4. Memory** | **Vector Quantized Latents** | Discrete tokens for long-term skill storage (VQ-VAE). |
| **5. Reflex** | **Safety Filter** | Hard-coded CBF constraints (collision, torque limits). |

