## 8. ⚠️ Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Mitigation Strategy |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Contraction Proof fails** | Fallback to **Input-to-State Stability (ISS)** which is less strict but still robust. |
| **CBF makes system too conservative** | Use **Learnable CBFs** where the safety function $h(x)$ is tuned via RL. |
| **Real-world latency too high** | Distill the Dynamic Graph into a smaller policy network for deployment (Teacher-Student). |
| **Hardware failure** | Rely heavily on **Isaac Gym** digital twin; real robot is only for validation. |

